		<title>Over 20,000 Volunteers Join International Legion to Fight Against Russia</title>
		<link>https://saveukraine.org/over-20000-volunteers-join-international-legion-to-fight-against-russia</link>
					<comments>https://saveukraine.org/over-20000-volunteers-join-international-legion-to-fight-against-russia#respond</comments>
		
